HOW TO USE SYMPHONY

INSTALLATION

After create your folder on your computer
exple: /Desktop/my_site


1- open terminal
2- NB: Place you to your folder with cd bfore installation

   composer create-project symfony/website-skeleton my-project ****

   (my-projet name is the folder wocontains all the symfony files)



DATABASE CONFIGURATION
open .env and edit:
DATABASE_URL=mysql://db_user:db_password@127.0.0.1:3306/db_name ***

db_user = database_username; exple: root, user, admin, steve
db_password = database_password; exple: root, user, admin, steve
db_name =  Database_namet


RUN WEBSITE

go to console
 php bin/console server:start 0.0.0.0:8000


 go to browser and paste http://127.0.0.1:8000 (it's generate by console)
